{"productOptionsHtml":"<div class=\"space-y-4 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-800\">\n<p class=\"text-neutral-600\">Use this section for <strong class=\"text-neutral-900\">ordering rules</strong>: style number, price band, minimums, and stated production time from the supplier catalog. Final invoice may reflect decoration, proofs, rush, or freight.</p>\n<table class=\"w-full border-collapse text-left text-[13px]\">\n<thead><tr class=\"border-b border-neutral-200 text-[11px] uppercase tracking-wide text-neutral-500\"><th class=\"py-2 pr-3 font-medium\">Field</th><th class=\"py-2 font-medium\">Value</th></tr></thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr class=\"border-b border-neutral-100\"><td class=\"py-2 pr-3 text-neutral-500 align-top\">Style #</td><td class=\"py-2 font-mono text-neutral-900\">1025</td></tr>\n<tr class=\"border-b border-neutral-100\"><td class=\"py-2 pr-3 text-neutral-500 align-top\">List price range</td><td class=\"py-2\">$3.14 – $3.39 USD</td></tr>\n<tr class=\"border-b border-neutral-100\"><td class=\"py-2 pr-3 text-neutral-500 align-top\">Minimum quantity</td><td class=\"py-2\">100</td></tr>\n<tr class=\"border-b border-neutral-100\"><td class=\"py-2 pr-3 text-neutral-500 align-top\">Stated production time</td><td class=\"py-2\">10 days</td></tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h4 class=\"text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-neutral-700 mt-5 mb-2\">Quantity pricing (USD)</h4>\n<p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600 mb-2\">Price per unit at each order-quantity break (from the live product page).</p>\n<table class=\"w-full border-collapse text-left text-[13px]\">\n<thead><tr class=\"border-b border-neutral-200 text-[11px] uppercase tracking-wide text-neutral-500\"><th class=\"py-2 pr-3 font-medium\">Quantity</th><th class=\"py-2 font-medium\">Price (each)</th></tr></thead>\n<tbody><tr class=\"border-b border-neutral-100\"><td class=\"py-2 pr-3 text-neutral-800 tabular-nums\">100</td><td class=\"py-2 tabular-nums\">$3.39 each</td></tr><tr class=\"border-b border-neutral-100\"><td class=\"py-2 pr-3 text-neutral-800 tabular-nums\">250</td><td class=\"py-2 tabular-nums\">$3.29 each</td></tr><tr class=\"border-b border-neutral-100\"><td class=\"py-2 pr-3 text-neutral-800 tabular-nums\">500</td><td class=\"py-2 tabular-nums\">$3.19 each</td></tr><tr class=\"border-b border-neutral-100\"><td class=\"py-2 pr-3 text-neutral-800 tabular-nums\">1000</td><td class=\"py-2 tabular-nums\">$3.14 each</td></tr></tbody>\n</table>\n<h4 class=\"text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-neutral-700 mt-5 mb-2\">Catalog highlights</h4><ul class=\"list-disc pl-5 space-y-1 text-[13px] leading-snug\"><li>Design your own wrapper</li><li>Engraved chocolate bar</li><li>Color wrapper on a 2&quot; x 5&quot; bar</li><li>Milk or dark chocolate</li><li>Add a Golden Ticket</li></ul>\n<div class=\"not-prose mt-5\">\n<h4 class=\"text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-neutral-700 mb-2\">Patch options (supplier)</h4>\n<p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600 mb-3\">Options and add-ons from the live Distributor Central product page for this SKU. Pricing may change; confirm on your quote.</p>\n<div class=\"overflow-hidden rounded-lg border border-neutral-200 bg-neutral-50/30\">\n<details class=\"group border-b border-neutral-200 last:border-b-0 open:bg-neutral-50/50\">\n<summary class=\"cursor-pointer list-none py-3 pl-1 pr-2 text-[13px] font-semibold text-neutral-900 outline-none [&::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden\">\n<span class=\"flex items-start justify-between gap-3\">\n<span>Product Color</span>\n<span class=\"mt-0.5 shrink-0 text-[10px] font-normal text-neutral-400 transition group-open:rotate-180\" aria-hidden=\"true\">▼</span>\n</span>\n</summary>\n<div class=\"border-t border-neutral-100 bg-white px-1 pb-3 pt-2\"><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">1025_BROWN</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">Brown</p></div></div>\n</details>\n<details class=\"group border-b border-neutral-200 last:border-b-0 open:bg-neutral-50/50\">\n<summary class=\"cursor-pointer list-none py-3 pl-1 pr-2 text-[13px] font-semibold text-neutral-900 outline-none [&::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden\">\n<span class=\"flex items-start justify-between gap-3\">\n<span>Engraved</span>\n<span class=\"mt-0.5 shrink-0 text-[10px] font-normal text-neutral-400 transition group-open:rotate-180\" aria-hidden=\"true\">▼</span>\n</span>\n</summary>\n<div class=\"border-t border-neutral-100 bg-white px-1 pb-3 pt-2\"><p class=\"text-[13px] text-neutral-700\">DI-1025-ENGRAVED</p></div>\n</details>\n<details class=\"group border-b border-neutral-200 last:border-b-0 open:bg-neutral-50/50\">\n<summary class=\"cursor-pointer list-none py-3 pl-1 pr-2 text-[13px] font-semibold text-neutral-900 outline-none [&::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden\">\n<span class=\"flex items-start justify-between gap-3\">\n<span>Additional Add-On</span>\n<span class=\"mt-0.5 shrink-0 text-[10px] font-normal text-neutral-400 transition group-open:rotate-180\" aria-hidden=\"true\">▼</span>\n</span>\n</summary>\n<div class=\"border-t border-neutral-100 bg-white px-1 pb-3 pt-2\"><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><div class=\"mb-2\"><img src=\"https://s3.distributorcentral.com/uploads/1/3/1362D0B2C5B1BA0A8F628FF212D2F1CA.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"max-h-28 max-w-[180px] rounded border border-neutral-200 object-contain\" loading=\"lazy\" /></div><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">Ticket</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">Golden Ticket</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-700\">Insert a &quot;golden ticket&quot; or a 1 or 2-sided full color perfect for any wrapper bar.</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[12px] font-medium text-neutral-800\">$0.99 each</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><div class=\"mb-2\"><img src=\"https://s3.distributorcentral.com/uploads/A/B/ABC18C922C43135C65BB970926B4EEA5.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"max-h-28 max-w-[180px] rounded border border-neutral-200 object-contain\" loading=\"lazy\" /></div><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">Hammer</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-700\">Include a Hammer?\nMake sharing easy and fun with custom-engraved hammers.  Perfect to add to a 1lb or 2lb solid bar.</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[12px] font-medium text-neutral-800\">$5.99 each · $6.99 each</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">Print</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">Printed Insert</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-700\">Card, Post Card, insert into any order</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[12px] font-medium text-neutral-800\">$0.99 each · $1.49 each</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><div class=\"mb-2\"><img src=\"https://s3.distributorcentral.com/uploads/A/C/AC8D7038262BD59FF784506EFCBF29EA.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"max-h-28 max-w-[180px] rounded border border-neutral-200 object-contain\" loading=\"lazy\" /></div><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">FullColor</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">Full Color Imprint on Chocolate</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-700\">Color Printing on Chocolate?\nLet your brand pop! Turn premium chocolate into edible art with bold, vibrant color! Available on Combo bars only.</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[12px] font-medium text-neutral-800\">$3.49 each · $4.49 each</p></div></div>\n</details>\n<details class=\"group border-b border-neutral-200 last:border-b-0 open:bg-neutral-50/50\">\n<summary class=\"cursor-pointer list-none py-3 pl-1 pr-2 text-[13px] font-semibold text-neutral-900 outline-none [&::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden\">\n<span class=\"flex items-start justify-between gap-3\">\n<span>Chocolate Flavors</span>\n<span class=\"mt-0.5 shrink-0 text-[10px] font-normal text-neutral-400 transition group-open:rotate-180\" aria-hidden=\"true\">▼</span>\n</span>\n</summary>\n<div class=\"border-t border-neutral-100 bg-white px-1 pb-3 pt-2\"><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">MILK</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">Chocolate - MILK</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">WHITE</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">Chocolate - White</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-700\">100% White Chocolate Solid Bars: 10% Upcharge</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">DARK</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">Chocolate - Dark</p></div></div>\n</details>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-500 mt-4\">Final quote may reflect selected options, proofs, rush, or freight beyond list pricing.</p>\n</div>","salesToolsHtml":"<div class=\"space-y-4 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-800\">\n<p><strong class=\"text-neutral-900\">Pitch this SKU</strong> — 2&quot;x 5&quot; Brand Impact Custom Chocolate Wrapper Bar. Lead with use case (uniforms, retail, teams, recognition), then minimums and timeline. Reference included services from “Price includes” in the Description tab when present (e.g. setup, virtual proof, shipping offers).</p>\n<ul class=\"list-disc pl-5 space-y-2\">\n<li>Quote style <span class=\"font-mono text-neutral-900\">1025</span> on proposals and POs.</li>\n<li>Offer virtual proofs and artwork checks before production.</li>\n<li>Cross-sell with hats, bags, or jackets for kit programs.</li>\n<li>For decoration and imprint methods, follow supplier notes in the Description tab.</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-500\">Approved partners can request internal sell sheets, comparison matrices, and margin guidance from the A Design Line team.</p>\n</div>","inventoryHtml":"<div class=\"space-y-3 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-800\">\n<p>Merchandise is <strong class=\"text-neutral-900\">typically sourced to order</strong>. Stock and availability may vary by supplier and season.</p>\n<p>Supplier-stated production window: <strong>10 days</strong> (not including transit).</p>\n<p>Contact the studio for <strong>rush</strong> feasibility, <strong>split shipments</strong>, or <strong>multi-location</strong> drops before placing large orders.</p>\n<p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-500\">Minimum order quantity: <strong class=\"text-neutral-800\">100</strong> units (per catalog line).</p>\n</div>"}